comment: An element of an ordinal class is ordinal. Proposition 7.6 of [TakeutiZaring] p. 36. This is an alternate proof of ~ ordelord using the Axiom of Regularity indirectly through ~ dford2 . dford2 is a weaker definition of ordinal number.
